While this does reduce the number of TOs, it really doesn't decrease 
the amount of PO recordkeeping. It just transfers the work from the 
Accountor to the Assessor. Someone still has to keep track of all those
voting debts.

This doesn't mean I am opposed to the change, just that I would like 
to see a small pay rise for the Assessor included in the Proposal, to
compensate em for the additional work.

